OL,7,FLast month just ahead of announcing
OL,8,Fhis appointment, immigration minister
OL,9,FSeema Malhotra confirmed around 64
OL,10,Fclaimants had died after applying for
OL,11,Fpayouts, as she set out the
OL,12,FGovernment's wish to speed up
OL,13,F"justice".
