OL,7,FOn Wednesday, she will attend an event
OL,8,Fwith Mr Foster where people affected
OL,9,Fby the scandal, which erupted in 2018
OL,10,Fwhen British citizens were wrongly
OL,11,Fdetained, deported or threatened with
OL,12,Fdeportation despite having the right
OL,13,Fto live in Britain, will hear from the
OL,14,Fcommissioner on his aims for his role.
OL,16,FA total of 10,326 claims had been made
OL,17,Funder the scheme as of May this year,
OL,18,Faccording to the latest Home Office
OL,19,Fdata.
