OL,7,FThe figures also showed that just over
OL,8,F#112 million has been paid out so far,
OL,9,Fcovering 3,334 claims.
OL,11,FIn an interview with the PA news
OL,12,Fagency ahead of the event, Mr Foster
OL,13,Fsaid he will be advocating for a
OL,14,F"fair, accessible and trauma-informed"
OL,15,Fcompensation scheme.
