OL,7,FWhile some campaigners have called for
OL,8,Fthe scheme to be moved out of the Home
OL,9,FOffice altogether, due to applicants'
OL,10,Flack of trust in the department, Mr
OL,11,FFoster appeared to disagree with such
OL,12,Fa change.
OL,14,FHe said: "I think what I will be
OL,15,Fpushing for is to make sure that this
OL,16,Fcompensation scheme must be seen to be
OL,17,Ffair, accessible and trauma-informed,
OL,18,Fand I will be pushing to get swifter
OL,19,Foutcomes.
OL,26,@vD@JOU
