OL,7,FHe said the department must show
OL,8,Fthrough actions rather than only words
OL,9,F"that there is going to be a culture
OL,10,Fchange".
OL,12,FMr Foster, a senior pastor at a
OL,13,FPilgrim Church in and the son of
OL,14,Fparents who migrated to the UK from
OL,15,FJamaica in 1959, said he will "be
OL,16,Freaching out to communities and acting
OL,17,Fas that advocate and trusted voice, as
OL,18,Fit were, going forward".
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@GO]wD@_OUzD@WO]
