OL,7,FAmong his top priorities will be
OL,8,Fensuring people are comfortable to
OL,9,Fcome forward and get the correct
OL,10,Fdocumentation to ensure they have
OL,11,Fsettled status and are not "wrongly
OL,12,Fclassified as illegal".
OL,14,FHe said: "People still need to feel
OL,15,Fthat they can be respected and
OL,16,Faccepted to come forward without that
OL,17,Ffear of being penalised as a result of
OL,18,Fnot having (the right documentation)."
