OL,7,FMeanwhile, Mr Foster said he will also
OL,8,Fbe working to ensure the legacy of the
OL,9,FWindrush generation is celebrated in
OL,10,Fthe future, including through the
OL,11,Fannual Notting Hill Carnival.
OL,13,FCampaigners last month called on the
OL,14,FGovernment to step in to protect the
OL,15,Ffuture of the west London carnival,
OL,16,Fwhich they said was in jeopardy, as
OL,17,Fthey asked for urgent funding to save
OL,18,Fthe world-famous event.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/13
