OL,7,FMr Foster said carnival "brings so
OL,8,Fmuch to the country, and I think that
OL,9,Fis an expression of the Windrush
OL,10,Fgeneration legacy".
OL,12,FHe added: "One of the things in my
OL,13,Frole would be to be looking to ensure
OL,14,Fthat we continue to celebrate the
OL,15,Flegacy and the contribution of the
OL,16,FWindrush generation, and carnival is
OL,17,Fone of those aspects, and I'll be
OL,18,Fhappy to engage in conversations to
OL,19,Flook at that going forward."
